Package: rap
Title: Generates Risk Assessment Plot and reclassification metrics
Version: 0.4
Authors@R: "John W Pickering <John.Pickering@otago.ac.nz>[aut, cre], Zoltan H
    Endre <z.endre@unsw.edu.au>[aut] and David Cairns
    <D.A.Cairns@leeds.ac.uk>[aut]"
Description: Calculates Net Reclassification Improvement (NRI) and Integrated
    Discrimination Improvement (IDI) metrics and plots Risk Assessment Plots
    (RAP). Includes category free and weighted NRI and uses bootstrapping to
    create confidence intervals.  Also compares AUCs with the De Long method.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    Hmisc,
    caret,
    pracma,
    pROC
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
LazyLoad: true
